page.title: 10Verwood clubs/associations.
page.content: There are many clubs in Verwood and the following are some of them:- Arts & Crafts, Badminton,Concert Brass, Bowling, Bridge, Carnival, Chamber of Trade, Cricket, Disabled, Dog Training, Dramatic, Pantomime, Evergreen, Football & Youth, Flower, Rangers, Guides,Brownies, Trefoil, Historical, Horticultural, NHR, Townswomens Guild, Wives, Women's Institute, WRVS, Leisure Centre, Memorial Hall, Netball, Parent Teacher/Hillside/C of E, Play Groups, Mother & Baby, Baby Sitting Service, Rambling, Ratepayers, Roller Skating, Royal British Legion, Cubs, Scouts, Venture Scouts, Tennis, Twinning, Viewpoint, Community, Wine, WRVS Luncheon Club, Village Youth Group, Methodist Youth Group, St. Michael's Youth Group, Darts. Ladies and Men's groups attached to churches.
